      <title>A Safe Haven</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This video examines Paige Braddock's artwork "The Great Smoky Mountains Church of Christ as a Beacon of Hope", which was inspired by the experiences of Helen Barnett during the Chimney Tops 2 Wildfires. Barnett, who is a member of Great Smoky Mountains Church of Christ in Pigeon Forge, remembered how the church helped folks who had lost everything. Survivors would show up at the church in shock, just needing to talk. Barnett and other volunteers at the church gave people food, blankets, whatever they could that might help. Listening to her talk made her imagine the church as a beacon, a safe haven in the communityâ€™s hour of need.</abstract>
